If you're anything like us, then a delicious hot sauce is something that truly makes you happy. We know the feeling, and that's why we crafted Happy Boy Hot Sauce to be your new go-to pepper sauce.

But if you've never tasted Happy Boy before, you may want to learn more about it before giving it a try for the first time. Let's discover why you should make room in your fridge or hot sauce collection for this premium, small batch hot sauce!

The Original Happy Boy is all about balance. Some hot sauces are garlic-heavy. Others have a strong vinegar profile. Some are just melt-your-face-off hot, while many are too mild with no substance. Take one taste of Happy Boy, though, and you’ll see why it’s different.

The Original Happy Boy balances a medium heat level with all the flavor notes you could want in a hot sauce. At first taste, you’ll experience the familiar tang of a vinegar-based pepper sauce that is quickly boosted with notes of fresh garlic. Then, a zesty, savory dimension takes the stage thanks to our proprietary 8-ingredient seasoning blend. Last but certainly not least, you’ll get a subtle sweetness from brown sugar. All of these flavor notes are tied together with the smooth taste of real butter.

It’s a balancing act that took a few years of passionate trial and error to get just right. But it's all worth it every time we see the look on people’s faces when they try Happy Boy Hot Sauce for the first time!

Mass-produced hot sauces may get the job done at an attractive price point, but take a look at the ingredients—so many off the shelf products today contain _seed oils, preservatives, and artificial flavorings._

You don’t need that garbage!

Don’t you think it’s time to improve your hot sauce collection with something delicious AND real? Here’s what’s in every bottle of Happy Boy:

items:
*Aged cayenne pepper sauce:*
_(aged red peppers, vinegar, salt, natural flavor, xanthan gum, garlic)_
    Every good hot sauce needs a strong foundation. Happy Boy uses a fermented cayenne base with a familiar flavor and heat level. But what about that xanthan gum? It's a safe, natural food-grade solution for thickening foods and emulsifying ingredients. Want to know more? We trust this article from Healthline:
*https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/xanthan-gum*
*Brown sugar:* No high fructose corn syrup here. Just good ol’ brown sugar!
*Garlic:* Plenty of freshly minced garlic goes into every batch of Happy Boy. You can actually see it in every bottle!

*Monosodium glutamate:*
    We’re passionate about our use of MSG in Happy Boy. MSG is a natural substance derived from the fermentation of molasses, sugar cane, sugar beets, and various starches. MSG is high in glutamic acid, which is naturally found in many popular ingredients including mushrooms, cheese, tomatoes, and more. Essentially, it’s a natural flavor enhancer that makes you go _'mmm!'_
*Spices:* Shh…it’s a secret! (But it’s all stuff you may have in your pantry right now!)

content.text: Our recipe is actually pretty simple when you look at it like that. But it’s the _precise balance_ of these elements that results in a truly unique hot sauce recipe that’s absolutely delicious, and enhances the taste of your food.

*Three Flavors to Try*
Did you know that Happy Boy comes in three flavors? In addition to the Original Happy Boy, there are two other versions to try:

items: *Garlic Parmesan Happy Boy:* What happens when you take the Original Happy Boy and add more garlic, freshly grated parmesan cheese (no anti-caking agents here), fresh parsley, and a healthy amount of butter? You get Garlic Parmesan Happy Boy! It has a mild heat level and a strong burst of savory, zesty flavor.

*Extremely Happy Boy:* If you like hotter hot sauces but still want great flavor, Extremely Happy Boy is for you. The recipe is the same as the Original, but with some Carolina Reaper peppers added to increase the heat level a few notches. Super flavorful and hot enough to grab your attention, Extremely Happy Boy hot sauce is a flavorful condiment to be reckoned with.

content.text: Whether you reach for the _Original_, the _Garlic Parm_, or the _Extremely_, Happy Boy hot sauces are sure to put a smile on your face! :)

*Are You Ready To Get Happy?*
Now that you know more about Happy Boy, are you ready to give it a try for yourself? Our goal is to put a smile on your face, every time you pour it on your favorite foods. Making it in small batches ensures every bottle is just right, so we hope you’ll give some a try.

Order some Happy Boy today, and *Get Happy!* Or, you can contact us with any questions you might have. Thank you for learning about hot sauce with us!
